zentinel-plane-description =
    Zentinel Control Plane provides the REST API and web dashboard for configuring Zentinel.

    Through the dashboard you can manage routes, upstream services, TLS certificates,
    ACME providers, and DNS plugins without editing configuration files directly.
    All changes are applied to Zentinel in real time.

zentinel-plane-features =
    - Web dashboard for Zentinel configuration
    - Route management (create, edit, delete routes)
    - Certificate management and renewal status
    - DNS provider configuration
    - Real-time configuration reload
